"rostro enim noceri non posse cognoverant; turribus autem excitatis tamen has altitudo puppium EX BARBARIS navibus superabat, ut neque ex inferiore loco satis commode tela adigi possent et missa a gallis gravius acciderent."|"ex barbaris navibus: of or on the barbarian skips. For this idiomatic use of ex, see ex muro, on the wall, p. 120,1. 19; ex itinere, on the march, p. 103,1. 18."

